      "description": "<p>Holding the rod used in the casting of the spell, you touch a Large or smaller chair that is unoccupied. The rod disappears, and the chair is transformed into a spelljamming helm (see “Magic Items” in the <i>Astral Adventurer's Guide</i>).</p>",
